begin_memory_text: Initially we introduced ourselves and I learned that my partner had cerebral palsy and we talked about how it affected him, especially during winter time when there is snow on the ground.
middle_memory_text: During the middle of the conversation we talked about what we liked to do for fun.  He asked if I was into sports to which I replied that I was not and he told me about his interest in sports.
end_memory_text: He told me that he really enjoyed our conversation and requested me to add him on  social media.  He was a very good person to speak with and I think I will find him on Facebook to become friends.
rest_of_day_open: I see the remainder of my week being relatively busy.  I need to prepare for a trial and included in that is conducting research on legal issues regarding virtual jury selection.  I am also expecting a new head boss to come into the office tomorrow so it will be a busy week.
critical_positive: I think everything worked well.  We were both respectful of each other and I thought his story was very good to hear.  He told me some of the struggles he's had dealing with cerebral palsy but he still carries on with his life and it was very inspiring to hear.
critical_negative: There truly was not anything that did not work well in our conversation.  Everything flowed well between topics and it was like we knew each other for longer than just a twenty five minute timed session.  He is a very admirable person and I applaud that he has such a positive attitude despite what he's had to deal with in life.

begin_memory_text: In the beginning of the conversation, we talk about what each other did for a living. We also talked about how we went to school and we did not feel that going to school was all that helpful with what we are doing now.
middle_memory_text: We talked about whether each other was a fan of sports. We also discussed simulators and how accurate they are nowadays. We talked about both of our experience with simulators that we have used.
end_memory_text: Towards the end of the conversation, we talked about whether each other had brothers and sisters. rest_of_day_open: This conversation has really given me a boost for the rest of the week. I feel like I have a lot more energy than I did an hour ago. critical_positive: It worked out well and that we were both able to keep each other engaged during the conversation.
